<br>
Die amazon scum<br>
<br>
::<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ut then e kept his sword drawn at her throat, but he grabbed her arm and licked her face. She hadn't even to think before she drew her extending pole from her pack and drew it to its full length.:::<br>
